Build a Java PowerPoint crawling module using LangChain4j that mirrors the 
existing PDF crawler module structure. Plugs into the same embeddings store 
and persistence framework.

## Context
- Existing modules: HTML crawler, PDF crawler (same pattern — follow it)
- This is a NEW standalone module: ppt-crawler
- Inject EmbeddingStore, EmbeddingModel, PersistenceService — do NOT reimplement
- Framework-agnostic: no Spring annotations, constructor injection only

