## Error Handling Rules
- .ppt legacy file → log warning with conversion instruction, skip, continue
- Password-protected .pptx → catch EncryptedDocumentException, skip
- Slide with zero text (image-only) → store chunk with 
  text="[IMAGE_ONLY_SLIDE_{n}]", set hasImages=true, continue
- Chart with no metadata → store "Chart present on slide {n}", continue
- Enrichment failure → fall back to raw text, never fail pipeline
- All errors → PipelineResult.errors list

## What NOT to build
- Do not extract or store images/thumbnails
- Do not support .ppt legacy binary format
- Do not build query/retrieval layer
- Do not reimplement embeddings store or persistence
- Do not add Spring annotations
